1. *Svetla* su me očarala u trenutku kada sam je prvi put ugledao. (The lights enchanted me the moment I saw it.)

2. Ona čuva *svetlu* nadu da će dobiti posao. (She keeps a bright hope of getting a job.)

3. *Svetli* svetli oči puni su nade. (Bright shining eyes are full of hope.)

4. Ona je nosila *svetlu* haljinu. (She was wearing a light dress.)

5. On je uzeo *svetlu* bateriju da bi proverio stanje. (He took a flashlight to check the condition.)